\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 This GitHub repository represents data from a collaboration between Jenifer Austin (Rutgers University Newark), Patrick Thane (University of Texas at Austin), Stephanie Rodr\'edguez (Rutgers University Newark) and Michele Goldin (Touro University). All data are owned by the authors and may not be used without permission. The data are shared anonymously across institutions.\
\

\f1\b0 This repository represents data collected from 120 participants attending a Spanish-English dual language immersion school using production and preference tasks. Participants\'92 command of gender agreement, volitional subjunctive, and differential object marking was tested. Data collection took place with two cohorts, in 2023 (cohort 1) and 2026 (cohort 2), and 30 children completed a longitudinal analysis at both time points. The following sections outline the subfolders in this repository and their functions.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf0 CSV Files subdirectory:
\f1\b0 \
There are multiple folders of CSV files here. All of these CSV files source from the two documents in the Master Files subfolder, which includes FCT Data.csv and Production Data.csv. There is also a former version of the production data code. These documents are updated directly from the Excel file called 
\f2\i Coding Document
\f1\i0  on the main directory. They are then fed into a coding loop described below under the Data Preparation subdirectory, which creates a series of additional CSV files.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
